    "Therefore, many institutes and universities have adopted these environments to provide online classes alongside traditional campus classes Hover and Wise (2022).",
    "These VLEs are considered more flexible and less expensive than traditional education, and students can submit their homework, participate in online discussions, and undertake exams.",
    "Moreover, these environments keep track of information for each student's learning process, such as how often a student logs into the system or accesses certain course materials and the time spent responding to the question.",
    "These activities lead VLEs to produce vast amounts of data, which can then be used to discover learning patterns and understand student needs Ángel F. Agudo-Peregrina et al (2014).",
    "Therefore, predicting student's academic performance is considered to be one of the most important indicators that evaluate the success of the educational process, as it can provide administrators and instructors with insights about students who may be at risk of failure or dropout and enable them to support these students as early as possible through tutoring, personalized learning experiences, feedback and guidance, and other forms of support Bañeres et al (2023); El-Sabagh (2021)."
